    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演一只被派往外太空的孤独兔子，踏上回家的旅程。抵御无休止的外星浪潮，采集珍贵资源，在压力下升级，并在能量枯竭中生存下来。每一次跃迁都让你离家更近一步……或者离毁灭更近一步。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044420/extras/843bb6027d516631d0ebf1fb3e95aa60.poster.avif?t=1767822462\" width=800 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044420/extras/843bb6027d516631d0ebf1fb3e95aa60.webm?t=1767822462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你所处的地方并不安全。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时不时会有成群的外星生物袭击你的飞船。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造<strong>防御设施</strong>，保持警惕，你就能活下去！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044420/extras/849ed81d9ecca9b876d6a64f50750d3f.poster.avif?t=1767822462\" width=1170 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044420/extras/849ed81d9ecca9b876d6a64f50750d3f.webm?t=1767822462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >资源有限，因此你必须不断地<strong>采集</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没错——时时刻刻都要采集。别偷懒！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044420/extras/e006e57e9490cfbe328ff8dd791bc258.poster.avif?t=1767822462\" width=800 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044420/extras/e006e57e9490cfbe328ff8dd791bc258.webm?t=1767822462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别忘了<strong>升级</strong>你的飞船！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以解锁许多实用的强化，让旅程变得稍微轻松一些。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044420/extras/28a354c766adefa7c4ed1aaa70af327e.poster.avif?t=1767822462\" width=1170 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044420/extras/28a354c766adefa7c4ed1aaa70af327e.webm?t=1767822462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索</strong>充满敌意的虚空，找到回家的路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
